name: FreeDollar
0:
”Alexa, ask Free Dollar how much is the Euro in Argentina”
”Alexa, ask Free Dollar what is the british pound rate in Argentina”
”Alexa, open Free Dollar and tell me the value of the Japanese Yen in united states”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: free dollar
des:
Free Dollar is a service for getting current currency exchange values in Argentina and the United States. It should be as simple as asking "How much is the Euro in Argentina" for Free Dollar to give you an accurate and current value for the Euro compared to the Argentine Peso.
This is a companion skill to the Android/iOS App Free Dollar.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
